'''Abdelatif Ramdane''' ({{langx|ar|عبد اللطيف رمضان}}, born 19 May 2001) is an Algerian professional footballer who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[MC Alger]] and the [[Algeria national football team|Algeria national team]].<ref name="abdelatif-ramdane" />

==Career==
===Club career===
During the 2019–20 season Abdelatif Ramdane was promoted to the adult category within [[MC Alger]]. On August 31, 2020, Ramdane joined [[JS Kabylie]] for three seasons.<ref>{{cite news|title=Le gardien de but Abdelatif Ramdane signe pour 3 ans à la JSK |url=https://www.competition.dz/actualites/89-ligue-1/73980-le-gardien-de-but-abdelatif-ramdane-signe-pour-3-ans-a-la-jsk.html |website=Competition |date=31 August 2020|access-date=8 June 2024}}</ref>

